<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> تُذْبَحُ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- فِي سَابِعِ وِلَادَتِهِ، وَيُسَمَّى فِيهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- فَإِنْ فَاتَ فَفِي أَرْبَعَةَ عَشَرَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- فَإِنْ فَاتَ فَفِي أَحَدٍ وَعِشْرِينَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَلَا تُعْتبَرُ الأَسَابِيعُ بَعْدَ ذَلِكَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَلَا يُكْسَرُ عَظْمُهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَطَبْخُهَا أَفْضَلُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَيَكُونُ مِنْهُ بِحُلْوٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَحُكْمُهَا كَأُضْحِيَّةٍ فِيمَا:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- يُجْزِئُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَيُسْتَحَبُّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَيُكْرَهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>لَكِنْ يُبَاعُ جِلْدٌ وَرَأْسٌ وَسَوَاقِطُ، وَيَتَصَدَّقُ بِثَمَنِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَإِنِ اتَّفَقَ وَقْتُ عَقِيقَةٍ وَأُضْحِيَّةٍ:</span> أَجْزَأَتْ إِحْدَاهُمَا عَنِ الأُخْرَى.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>